Represents a user obtained from /api/users?name=<username> or /api/users/<uniqueId>

Represents a selected badge as part of the User object

Represents a friend obtained from /api/users/<uniqueId>/friends
UserGroup

UserProfile
Represents a profile obtained from /api/users/<uniqueId>/profile (contains user, groups, badges, friends and rooms)
UserRoom
